{"tid":902152,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【衝破心理關口】岑潔儀第二胎臨盆在即 全裸抱大仔影孕照","createTime":"2018-11-14T14:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T15:20:05.000Z","uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2634f29dacb00ef255ac8fb168689bfb6806a317","tid":902152,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181114/large/1542192542_d494.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181114%2Flarge%2F1542192542_d494.jpg&h=cc71fc5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岑潔儀話影裸照，老公冇眼睇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181114/large/1542192542_5afa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181114%2Flarge%2F1542192542_5afa.jpg&h=9a51c0b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岑潔儀話老公Dixon請咗假陪佢生仔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181114/large/1542192542_79ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181114%2Flarge%2F1542192542_79ff.jpg&h=623bb6d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岑潔儀抱住大仔影全裸孕照。<br />\n<br />\n31歲嘅岑潔儀（Zoey），15年為馬來西亞老公Dixon誕下囝囝Damian，今年5月宣佈再陀B。就嚟生得嘅Zoey，早前仲同囝囝影咗一輯尺度好大嘅全裸孕照，全裸上陣嘅佢側身企，再抱住3歲大囝囝，十分温馨。<br />\n<br />\nZoey話：「身邊好多朋友第一胎都影咗大肚裸照，但嗰時我覺得好尷尬冇影，今次第二胎決定放膽影。」講到老公有冇咩意見？佢就講笑話老公冇眼睇。呢胎都係陀仔嘅Zoey話，老公11月會休假陪伴在右，而佢就會準備好餵哺母乳，會搵專業人士幫忙催乳。"},{"pid":"1c13bf77098dcbb2e5077c811c73e94047b5fe08","tid":902152,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f24fecf23afbf4624f2935e5e5ea9ebc92bd89f","tid":902152,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:59:21.000Z","msg":"龍舟掛鼓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c552085b463fc217d5a8c6a9cac3a4b6c796839d","tid":902152,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d215d6143f2bfa5d9c2d637847c5f77ee9891036","tid":902152,"uid":53736,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"仆街好撚恐怖 好似進擊巨人d奇行種兩母子"},{"pid":"fc1255d9dc4aa15444a71bb71ab77f6e8c8feca4","tid":902152,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:20:05.000Z","msg":"個仔似5歲"}]}